#: ../../source/functions/input/mouse.md:13
msgid "The FlexDesigner exposes the following settings for this key:"
msgstr "FlexDesigner 为此按键提供以下设置："

#: ../../source/functions/input/mouse.md:15
msgid ""
"Buttons: Includes the 'Left', 'Right', 'Middle', 'Back', and 'Forward' "
"checkboxes. These specify if any of those buttons should be pressed in "
"the mouse event."
msgstr ""
"按钮：包括"左键"、"右键"、"中键"、"后退"和"前进"复选框。这些指定在鼠标事件中是否应该按下这些按钮中的任何一个。"

#: ../../source/functions/input/mouse.md:16
msgid ""
"Movement: Specify how much the mouse should move when triggered. The "
"'wheel' and 'pan' specifies the movement of the vertical scroll wheel and"
" the horizontal scroll wheel respectively."
msgstr ""
"移动：指定触发时鼠标应该移动多少。"滚轮"和"平移"分别指定垂直滚轮和水平滚轮的移动。"

#: ../../source/functions/input/mouse.md:17
msgid ""
"Absolute Position: When checked, the movement would be sent as absolute "
"movement instead of relative. Which means the mouse would be moved to the"
" specified location, instead of move by the specified distance."
msgstr ""
"绝对位置：选中时，移动将作为绝对移动而不是相对移动发送。这意味着鼠标将移动到指定位置，而不是按指定距离移动。"

#: ../../source/functions/input/mouse.md:18
msgid "Double Click: Check if the click needs to be a double click"
msgstr "双击：检查点击是否需要是双击"

#: ../../source/functions/input/mouse.md:19
msgid ""
"Release After Click: Check if the mouse buttons should be released after "
"click. Otherwise, the mouse button would be in the pressed state"
msgstr ""
"点击后释放：检查点击后是否应该释放鼠标按钮。否则，鼠标按钮将处于按下状态"

#: ../../source/functions/input/mouse.md:21
msgid "On the Flexbar"
msgstr "在 Flexbar 上"

#: ../../source/functions/input/mouse.md:23
msgid "Press the key on the Flexbar to trigger the defined action."
msgstr "在 Flexbar 上按下按键以触发定义的操作。"

